The Concept:
   To give the Hotel Helpdesk person the ability to check 
and search for a room and reserve one to a client base 
on the room Category and price range. 



Brainstorming:

   Functions 
         @ book a room
         @ free a room
         @ search for a room  
         @ Auto pricing rooms
@ we can set a discount to be apply to all rooms in 
X Category between two dates of Reservation 

@ rooms Category.. standard, Suite, number of bedroom. 
 Number of bathroom 
   
      




